ns0:DescribedValueSet.ns0:Purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values identifies the location or environment of a patient as an acute care hospital.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify the location or environment of a patient as an acute care hospital. Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the Transfer category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Only use codes which represent the location or environment of a patient as an acute care hospital.
